      <div class="flex-grow-1 rounded overflow-hidden" id="clipboard-787238ea0c871f815afe5de2ac434a10"><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># Отмонтировать и очистить USB-накопитель.</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">umount /dev/sdX* <span class="o">&amp;&amp;</span> sgdisk -Z /dev/sdX
